Now, popular tools for this are Google surveys and SurveyMonkey.

00:04:41.889 --> 00:04:45.849
Google surveys allows you to access a readily available focus group.

00:04:45.850 --> 00:04:47.780
You get numerous results rather

00:04:47.779 --> 00:04:50.704
quickly based on the questions that you're hoping to answer.

00:04:50.704 --> 00:04:53.839
In fact, you may have seen these types of survey questions pop

00:04:53.839 --> 00:04:57.229
up as ads before watching a YouTube video.

